Open Server:

./echoserver (wr or rp)

example: ./echoserver wr

Open client:

./client (rclient or wclient) portnumber rate filename directory timeout 

example: ./client rclient 54621 1 file.txt ohaio 1


Each thread of the 'Writer' generates 2 mb text and writes it to the textfile.

Each thread of the 'Reader' reads the text from textfile, creates new file in the directory and writes copied text.

The semaphores are used to solve Reader-Writer problem. 
